                Connect with verified, reliable maids for all your household needs
            </p>
            <button class="bg-white text-purple-700 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg hover:shadow-xl transition pulse-animation">
                <i class="fas fa-search mr-2"></i>Find Your Helper Now
